title: etnies Chris Del Moro artshow at ECHO store Biarritz
description: In the middle of the European high summer season etnies brought an fundraiser event “LOVE YOUR PLANET” to Biarritz. This ecological-surf-art event starring etnies’ surfer and artist, Chris del Moro, was about sharing passion and creativity. All art sale during “LOVE YOUR PLANET” will benefit the etnies “buy a shoe, plant a tree” program in Costa Rica.
